original_title: 2010 NCAA Basketball Regional Semi-Finals: Kansas State vs. Xavier
overview: The season may be over, but the legacy continues. Kansas State posted one of their most impressive seasons in 2009-2010. Hailed as one of the greatest NCAA Tournament games of all-time, this DVD features the commercial-free broadcast as the Kansas State Wildcats battled the Xavier Musketeers into double overtime on their way to the win and 2010 appearance in the Elite Eight.
title: 2010 NCAA Basketball Regional Semi-Finals: Kansas State vs. Xavier
